      "body" : "@shanyangqu Sadly, no.  <code>clean</code> is in a <a href=\"http://maven.apache.org/guides/introduction/introduction-to-the-lifecycle.html#Lifecycle_Reference\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">separate lifecycle</a>, so it&#39;s not called by default."
