      "body" : "@JunchenLiu There are actually four items named <code>clean</code>: <code>clean</code> lifecycle with its <code>clean</code> phase, <code>clean</code> <a href=\"https://maven.apache.org/guides/introduction/introduction-to-plugin-prefix-mapping.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">prefix</a> for the  <code>maven-clean-plugin</code> with its <code>clean</code> goal. See also the comment to <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/41466540/1744774\">this answer to <i>Maven: Lifecycle vs. Phase vs. Plugin vs. Goal</i></a>."
